Enum AssessmentPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AssessmentPoint>
      • org.jmisb.api.klv.st1108.st1108_3.AssessmentPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<AssessmentPoint>, IKlvValue, IInterpretabilityQualityMetadataValue

    public enum AssessmentPoint
extends Enum<AssessmentPoint>
implements IInterpretabilityQualityMetadataValue
    Assessment Point.

    An Assessment Point is a physical location along the imaging workflow. The Assessment Point item documents the calculation of one or more metrics at this location. The Assessment Point is an enumerated value. This Local Set item is mandatory.
